{"obj_edit_time":"1707027778","blocks":[{"block_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd","block_type":1,"children":["doxcnjFYR8liQU66T9jZy8Olpsj","doxcnzCL517yGAvBJAxZRK5zEed","Jl3Cdiw6PoWdDDxvG40cicXpnXo","WSZvdSwnbofebKxukiYcQC8LnPe","LnzWdmhMYo9GoKxDm7NcvExFnqe","Qk4AdiGzSoJ8rpxtSqqcRZV5nEf","Zrrgdws5qoydKwxZgOwcYHzEnvh","ESfSd9YYhoKTZ9xdzE8ctn9mnsS","doxcnqUUGuQmB5ui7Z6WM8O1J8d","doxcnGS2BCNYOq8psneAb5q4bec","SKfzdSSbvo3UX2x5JoqchTRVnIg","YxYGd3H8ioeRrixYgp4cyGaJnZ3","LRhzdssxgoQPuUx3TnJcOVGXnz4","H7a3dGZaqomerIxZ9cbcqFIKnCd","Kdjbd3MN8oGSyFxAAcpcm4yDnVb","PvtodVX0No1kVmxanRQcvsLOnCb","W4aJdUsuyoxGUVxEvZ0c9nvWnXd","H3hFd11pboK4gBxisGgcJBL5nSf","FP2XdeGR1ol6NYxk5SMcELAlnrg","RswMdrO3aoz2rSx3ZK8cmA7bnid","D8a2dGAiuo3adfxoRMxcUO2tn9c","doxcnHCyOz1Dgp6NMf7PgJFzhpd"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"doxcnjFYR8liQU66T9jZy8Olpsj","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"概述","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"doxcnzCL517yGAvBJAxZRK5zEed","block_type":2,"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在證券行業，\"轉倉業務\"通常指的是投資者將其持有的證券（股票、債券等）從一個經紀商或帳戶轉移到另一個的過程。這可能是由於多種原因，包括投資策略的變化、經紀商服務的不滿意、費用優勢等。以下是有關證券行業轉倉業務的簡要介紹：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"Jl3Cdiw6PoWdDDxvG40cicXpnXo","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"投資組合調整： 投資者可能會根據市場條件、風險偏好或其他投資目標調整其投資組合。這可能涉及到賣出一些證券並購入其他證券，從而實現投資組合的重新平衡。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"WSZvdSwnbofebKxukiYcQC8LnPe","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"經紀商選擇： 投資者可能選擇更換經紀商，這可能是因為他們尋求更低的交易佣金、更好的客戶服務、更先進的交易平台或其他因素。在這種情況下，投資者需要將其現有的證券頭寸從原有的經紀商帳戶中轉移到新的帳戶。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"LnzWdmhMYo9GoKxDm7NcvExFnqe","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"費用優勢： 不同的經紀商可能對交易收費有所不同。投資者可能會選擇將其證券頭寸轉移到收費更低的經紀商，以減少交易成本。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"Qk4AdiGzSoJ8rpxtSqqcRZV5nEf","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"地理位置： 投資者有時可能考慮將證券頭寸轉移到更靠近其居住地或業務地點的經紀商，以方便監控和管理投資。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"Zrrgdws5qoydKwxZgOwcYHzEnvh","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"服務不滿意： 投資者可能因為對當前經紀商的服務不滿意而決定轉移其證券頭寸。這可能包括對執行質量、客戶支持或其他服務方面的不滿。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"ESfSd9YYhoKTZ9xdzE8ctn9mnsS","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"稅務考慮： 在進行證券頭寸的轉倉時，投資者還需要考慮潛在的稅務影響。某些交易可能會觸發資本利得稅，因此投資者可能需要謹慎考慮轉倉的時機，以最小化稅務負擔。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"doxcnqUUGuQmB5ui7Z6WM8O1J8d","block_type":2,"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"總體而言，證券行業的轉倉業務是投資者根據各種因素調整其證券頭寸的一種策略性決策。這需要仔細考慮市場條件、費用結構、服務質量等多個因素，以確保轉倉過程順利進行。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxcnGS2BCNYOq8psneAb5q4bec","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"證券取出注意事項","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"SKfzdSSbvo3UX2x5JoqchTRVnIg","block_type":2,"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在證券取出過程中，券商主要執行以下關鍵步驟：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"YxYGd3H8ioeRrixYgp4cyGaJnZ3","block_type":2,"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"確定轉入標的","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"LRhzdssxgoQPuUx3TnJcOVGXnz4","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"與客戶確認好轉入的證券細節，如所屬券商、證券明細、轉倉數量、成本價等","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"H7a3dGZaqomerIxZ9cbcqFIKnCd","block_type":2,"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"聯絡對方券商","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"Kdjbd3MN8oGSyFxAAcpcm4yDnVb","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"確認好本次轉倉的細節後，需要及時與對方券商聯繫了解轉移流程，如需要填寫一些表格或提供特定的文件等，以確保證券標的可以正常的交接","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"PvtodVX0No1kVmxanRQcvsLOnCb","block_type":2,"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"券商的义务还包括：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"W4aJdUsuyoxGUVxEvZ0c9nvWnXd","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"了解費用和手續費","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 在進行轉移之前，了解目標券商可能收取的任何費用和手續費。這可能包括轉移費用、帳戶關閉費用等。確保你理解並願意支付這些費用。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"H3hFd11pboK4gBxisGgcJBL5nSf","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"核實目標券商的支持股票類型","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 不是所有券商都支持相同類型的股票或投資產品。確保你的目標券商支持你想要轉移的具體股票或投資品種。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"FP2XdeGR1ol6NYxk5SMcELAlnrg","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"確認帳戶持有人信息","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 確保你在源券商和目標券商的帳戶上的個人信息匹配，以避免可能的問題。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"RswMdrO3aoz2rSx3ZK8cmA7bnid","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"處理開市時間","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 股票市場只在特定的時間段內開市。確保你的轉移請求是在股市開市期間進行，以便及時處理。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"D8a2dGAiuo3adfxoRMxcUO2tn9c","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"慎重處理開倉頭寸","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 如果你有未平倉的頭寸，要考慮市場波動可能對這些頭寸產生的影響。在股票轉移之前，確保你已經仔細考慮並決定如何處理這些頭寸。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"},{"block_id":"doxcnHCyOz1Dgp6NMf7PgJFzhpd","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"保留交易記錄","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"： 在轉移過程中，保留所有相關的交易記錄和文件。這些文件可能在未來證明你在股票轉移過程中的活動和決策。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"BcJsdZyL3oFk2HxCLfocrmY1nSd"}]}